OUS By Island Card: Lo mbiko ufingqa amaphesenti emisebenzi edlula ukusetshenziswa kolwandle ngabantu abahlala eziqhingini, njengoba kubikwe kuNhlolovo Yokusetshenziswa Kolwandle. Izinhlelo kufanele zicabangele umthelela ongaba khona emikhakheni uma ukufinyelela noma imisebenzi ikhawulelwe.
OUS By Island Card - learn more:
‚ÑπÔ∏è Uhlolojikelele: ukuze kuthathwe inani elibekwa umkhakha ngamunye ezindaweni ezihlukene zasogwini, kwenziwe inhlolovo yokusetshenziswa kolwandle. Abantu bahlonze imikhakha ababamba iqhaza kuyo, futhi bacelwa ukuthi badwebe izindawo abazisebenzisayo uma beqhathaniswa nalowo mkhakha futhi banikeze ukubaluleka kokubaluleka. Izimpendulo ngazinye zibe sezihlanganiswa ukuze kukhiqizwe amamephu okushisa ahlanganisiwe ngomkhakha. Lokhu kuvumela inani lezindawo ukuthi zilinganiswe, zifinyezwe, futhi ziqhathaniswe nezinye njengezibaluleke kakhulu noma ngaphansi.

Inani libe selisetshenziswa njengommeleli wokukala ukulahleka komnotho okungaba khona emikhakheni ebangelwa ukudalwa izindawo ezivikelwe. Lo mbiko ungasetshenziswa ukunciphisa umthelela ongaba khona wohlelo emkhakheni, kanye nokuhlonza nokunciphisa ukungqubuzana phakathi kwezinjongo zokongiwa kwemvelo nemisebenzi yomkhakha. Ukuphakama kwenani lenani ngaphakathi kohlelo, kuba mkhulu umthelela ongaba khona endaweni yokudoba uma ukufinyelela noma imisebenzi ikhawulelwe.

Qaphela, imephu yokushisa ewumphumela imelela kuphela abantu abahloliwe.

Lo mbiko ubonisa amaphesenti yenani elibanzi le-EEZ labadobi bakulesi siqhingi eliqukethwe uhlelo oluseduze nogu.
